rows.label: qst400108_msg0001
rows.name:
Rex back again?
Did friend forget something?

rows.label: qst400108_msg0002
rows.name:
No, I didn't exactly forget anything.
I just decided to make a cash transfer.

rows.label: qst400108_msg0003
rows.name:
Rex find money on floor? Nopon round
here very particular about money, so
should turn in even small change!

rows.label: qst400108_msg0004
rows.name:
No, I didn't pick up any small change...
Actually, I got my hands on a big sum.

rows.label: qst400108_msg0005
rows.name: Big sum? Like 2,000G?

rows.label: qst400108_msg0006
rows.name:
I'd rather not bandy the number
about too much, but...

rows.label: qst400108_msg0007
rows.name: More like a hundred thousand.

rows.label: qst400108_msg0008
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]HUNDRED THOUSAND?!!!!!!

rows.label: qst400108_msg0009
rows.name: [ML:Feeling ]Not so loud...!

rows.label: qst400108_msg0010
rows.name: Oh. Yes. Sorry much!

rows.label: qst400108_msg0011
rows.name: But where Rex get all that gold...?

rows.label: qst400108_msg0012
rows.name:
Actually no. No need to tell Melolo!
Melolo not want get mixed up in
shady business!

rows.label: qst400108_msg0013
rows.name: I don't think it's that big of a deal...

rows.label: qst400108_msg0014
rows.name:
Anyhoodles, Rex. Melolo not able to
accept such large sum here anyway.
Should take directly to courier.

rows.label: qst400108_msg0015
rows.name:
All monies Melolo accept here
always delivered through courier
called Max.

rows.label: qst400108_msg0016
rows.name: Oh, OK! Max, I know him.

rows.label: qst400108_msg0017
rows.name:
I didn't know he was also delivering
the money for me all this time... Huh!

rows.label: qst400108_msg0018
rows.name:
Well, this certainly make things quicker!
Friend know where to find Max?

rows.label: qst400108_msg0019
rows.name:
Yeah, he'll be just through the
Avaritia Bazaar, right?
Thanks, Melolo!

rows.label: qst400108_msg0101
rows.name:
Friend not know where to find
courier Max after all?

rows.label: qst400108_msg0102
rows.name:
Instead of go up main staircase to
Chairman's Room, go down small
steps to right instead.

rows.label: qst400108_msg0103
rows.name:
Then friend see Whiteside Salvaging
shop. Max right next to that.
